data.description: Charming, cul-da-sac home loaded with contemporary updates! New hardwood and tile throughout majority of home, NO carpet! Kitchens redesigned space has granite countertops, new backsplash, sink, hardware, dishwasher and faucet offering both style and practicality. Walk in pantry provides additional storage. Refrigerator conveys. Expanding the footprint of the home, an added sitting area at the back beckons with the promise of a peaceful space and cozy retreat.  Enjoy elegant light fixtures in every space w/ added recessed lighting. Laundry room has added cabinetry with countertop space making chores easier & is conveniently located off primary suite. Primary offers jetted soaking tub, large shower, split closets, new countertops coming soon. All toilets in home have been upgraded. New roof 2021 w/ added gutters and French drain extensions. Nestled on a pie-shaped corner lot, with ample back yard space'an unexpected luxury in such an established neighborhood. The yard, a canvas of possibilities, is fully fenced and ready to envision an added patio space to extend entertaining outdoors. So many upgrades to list. Truly a GEM in this market & a must see! Agents see remarks. 2024-01-17
